                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>At a meeting at Frankfurt on November 4, the United States, United Kingdom, and
                    French Military Governors for Germany briefly discussed the question of
                    reparations policy. For records of the proceedings of the meeting, see the notes
                    prepared by Ambassador <persName corresp="#p_MRD1">Murphy</persName> and
                    telegram 2686, November 5, from Berlin, <ref target="#pg_434">pages 434</ref>
                    and <ref target="#pg_438">438</ref>.</p>
            </div>
